{"tid":215413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保良局訓練營】報道指中四生被嚇寫花file冇書讀 出營患抑鬱症","createTime":"2017-04-24T11:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T12:55:59.000Z","uid":45967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b91cb282868df1f360b021693b2e51bad0fbf47","tid":215413,"uid":45967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170424/large/1493003232_55ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170424%2Flarge%2F1493003232_55ef.jpg&h=acda797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保良局領袖紀律訓練營近月爆出多宗涉虐待學生醜聞，保良局月中發聲明宣佈與承辦機構「導航訓練中心」達成協議決定解約，目前沒有舉辦任何領袖紀律訓練營活動；《明報》頭版今日報道指，有學生一年多前參加保良局訓練營期間，遭教練及總監對她連番喝罵，揚言要她「無書讀」，該名學生事後患上抑鬱症。<br />\n<br />\n報道指張同學（化名）2015年底讀中四時在學校安排下參加該4日3夜訓練營，入營第一日全班學生遭教練梁永樂批評「讀書有什麼用？什麼都做不來」。獲選為班會主席的她又被問道「班中有沒有一些欠交功課的人」，她回應「沒有」，結果被教練大罵「你講大話，你班中有常欠交功課的人」、「你不了解同學，做什麼班會主席」。<br />\n報道又指張同學曾以不舒服為由拒絕參加活動並要求離營，教練卻回覆「離營就要退學」；訓練營項目總監盧錦昌聽到她要求離營更向她喝道「要致電教育局，寫花你的file，你會無書讀，全港不會有學校收你」。<br />\n報道指保良局發言人稱未接獲同學的相關投訴，有關學校正嘗試向2015年參加訓練營的同學了解。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n友情連結：<a href=\"https://katouotome.wordpress.com/2017/03/19/anti-po-leung-kuk-concentration-camps/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkatouotome.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2Fanti-po-leung-kuk-concentration-camps%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=60ed7afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://katouotome.wordpress.com/2017/03/19/anti-po-leung-kuk-concentration-camps/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa50d12cb4fd1ce10df4b0213e846f3c3ee2a64","tid":215413,"uid":87575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88175e860a46b944f189e43327e44d6f0ecac799","tid":215413,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"4f48adf25571d6eaed65505bfba550daa803b7dc","tid":215413,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"之前仲死口唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e32761d4272d9e3ed888684862c61e3269820f2","tid":215413,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637791d1edc1ef7a13900422f7fd3700e742553e","tid":215413,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"我一早講學生自殺同保良局可能有關<br />\n近年多學童自殺同近年on9營成正比關係"},{"pid":"9febb4afa4ad9546682d98a432e6f369148077ac","tid":215413,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dcf20e0b3042d2aa90c93ed1680ff897216477","tid":215413,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲柒頭淨係識欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}